item.title: Reinterpretation of the Dynamics of Urban Renewal Based on Multiple Rent Gaps: Taking Langyuan Vintage and Tianzifang as Examples
item.description: Abstract # Under the requirement of limited or even negative urban land increment, understanding the motivations for urban regeneration and promoting sustainable regeneration practices constitute crucial issues in the contemporary planning studies.
